  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Career Program for Recovering Addicts in Hillsboro</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Some women enter our eight bed recovery house with no concept of how to live life on life&apos;s terms. One of the tools we would like to provide them is how to choose and pursue the career of their choice.  This project will supply residents with training, mentorship, supplies, and financial support to reach the career goals they have set. Through this program we believe that we can help women who have struggled with this disease  to conquer addiction and become productive members of society.</narrative>
  </description>
